      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "やはり皆さん、大好きなグミを用意していたんですね\nこれ、私からです。味が被っていないといいのですが",
      "startTime": 18.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "本当？　ありがとう、沙季。被りは気にしないで\nグミはいくつあってもいいもの。同じ味でも大歓迎よ",
      "startTime": 28.4478900273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
